name: Doula Orlando
tag_list: doula, birthing, naturalbirth, homebirth, waterbirth, home-birth, natural-birth
overview:
Doula Orlando is home to the CBI trained birth professional Bethanie Stardust. The site includes articles related to child birth, child rearing, holistic living and intuitive parenting from a number of contributors.

Those seeking information regarding doulas and their role in birth, or the process of home births, natural births or water births would likely find this site a good resource for further information or to seek further information from the site owner.
